title: [Zul Logoth, Cave of Wisdom]
description: Whispering winds can be heard coming from hidden vents in the dark, craggy ceiling, circulating crisp, cool air in this cave.  Rotten logs litter the floor, their soft flesh breaking underfoot, host to numerous orange oyster mushrooms and glowing purple toadstools that thrive on the decomposing wood.  The prevalent smell of decay is not entirely unpleasant.
